{"tid":578191,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"累翻了！新垣結衣驚傳「已到極限」　下半年將請長假休息","createTime":"2018-03-02T11:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T12:20:37.000Z","uid":9573,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"f7d1d580777ee0242728083a93e4b2839c63757d","tid":578191,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:53:47.000Z","msg":"日本女星新垣結衣人氣一直高居不下，憑藉著《月薪嬌妻》再創下事業高峰，甜美的外型也擄獲眾多粉絲，日前被網友票選為「最理想的女朋友」，更被暱稱為「國民老婆」。新垣結衣工作、代言接不完讓她過度疲勞，據傳她下半年已向經紀公司申請長假，好好休息。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/03/01/1263171-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F1263171-XXL.jpg&h=ed0b83f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲日本女星新垣結衣擁有甜美外型，人氣高居不下。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n新垣結衣在今年6月即將滿30歲，除了《Code Blue》（空中急診英雄）電影版7月要上映之外，更傳出《月薪嬌妻》要開拍續集。日本化妝品牌KOSE近日也曝光新廣告，找來新垣結衣加持人氣，她身穿白色上衣配牛仔短褲，清新的打扮讓網友直呼「戀愛了」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/03/01/1263170-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F03%2F01%2F1263170-XXL.jpg&h=76aecf9f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n▲新垣結衣接拍KOSE新廣告，穿著清新簡約。<br />\n<br />\n據香港《蘋果日報》報導，新垣結衣雖然登上事業高峰，影片、廣告接拍不完，但也讓當年古巨基、古天樂、吳家樂、劉愷威、何遠恆五人，被合稱為「新五虎將」，事隔23年，五虎的其中四虎終於重聚，古巨基在社交網甫出與古天樂、吳家樂及劉愷威的世紀合照，更留言話：「四虎二十四年後合體！Calling何遠恆～」她身心俱疲，外傳她的工作讓她「已到極限」，想在30歲之前好好休息，下半年已向經紀公司請長假。"},{"pid":"eee49435651c0c1a2d4fb1754d07ea7f86721393","tid":578191,"uid":93394,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:55:21.000Z","msg":"乜鳩五虎"},{"pid":"840951d9b4b66b545fee9db9cbb925234914fa1b","tid":578191,"uid":174098,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:56:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">但也讓當年古巨基、古天樂、吳家樂、劉愷威、何遠恆五人，被合稱為「新五虎將」，事隔23年，五虎的其中四虎終於重聚，古巨基在社交網甫出與古天樂、吳家樂及劉愷威的世紀合照，更留言話：「四虎二十四年後合體！Calling何遠恆～」</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63393140cec79875e3c1772b16799d71d4651d29","tid":578191,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:56:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4937dc4042020a8dcf9796ddc9bc9a7ff9e19a3a","tid":578191,"uid":174098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:58:24.000Z","msg":"btw 結衣BB休養多啲 唔好操壞身子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465a50bef0d27b3b255f4bf1d02ff959872d5b4b","tid":578191,"uid":27163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T11:59:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">那</span></span>"},{"pid":"c21468e2fcd34079d4e7b94c6b97fe4888a4d9c2","tid":578191,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"有左？"},{"pid":"baf92b0d67e24607f26b30ebe74258ab4d363c9a","tid":578191,"uid":76470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c21468e2fcd34079d4e7b94c6b97fe4888a4d9c2","tid":578191,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"有左？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:02:14.000Z","msg":"那個了哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c9d7572a7926677ea3c1ea2aa834efc4b85d056","tid":578191,"uid":10876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"baf92b0d67e24607f26b30ebe74258ab4d363c9a","tid":578191,"uid":76470,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c21468e2fcd34079d4e7b94c6b97fe4888a4d9c2","tid":578191,"uid":2155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:00:08.000Z","msg":"有左？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:02:14.000Z","msg":"那個了哦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/02/201154_ce5162fa7a820d7d064c93680a34a0e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumb